description: This file contains implementation of a platform-dependent utility function for creating a DSL Home Model Object Record, including licensing information, documentation, and the function DslhCreateObjRecord that instantiates the object.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE DslhCreateObjRecord(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates and returns a new DSL Home Model Object Record using the underlying object creation function DslhObjroCreate.
